<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Vihaan's Vision</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css?v=20260716" />
  <script src="/page-views.js?v=20260716-2" defer></script>
</head>
<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Vihaan's Vision home">
    <span class="logo-mark">☀️</span>
    <span class="logo-copy">
      <strong>Vihaan's Vision</strong>
      <small>A world where every child smiles</small>
    </span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/" style="color:#2f6f9f">Home</a><a href="/events/">Events</a><a href="/donate/">Donate</a><a href="/donation-events/">Donation Events</a><a href="/testimonials/">Testimonials</a><a href="/team/">Team</a><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a>
  </nav>
</header>


<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker">Tiny creations. Real joy.</span>
      <h1>Small gifts.<br>Big smiles.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Hi, I’m Vihaan. I started this project because I believe every child deserves
        a reason to smile. I make 3D-printed keychains, toys, and small gifts, and I also
        teach AI classes for kids to help raise money for printing materials.
      </p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/events/">AI Classes & Events</a>
        <a class="btn gold" href="https://hcb.hackclub.com/donations/start/vihaan-s-vision" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Support My Mission</a>
        <a class="btn light" href="/donation-events/">See Donation Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-art" aria-label="Smiling sun illustration">
      <div class="orbit"></div>
      <div class="hero-sun">😊</div>
      <div class="floating-note note-1">AI classes</div>
      <div class="floating-note note-2">3D printed gifts</div>
      <div class="floating-note note-3">Smiles</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">What I Do</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      I use creativity, technology, and kindness to turn small ideas into gifts for children.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-3">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>I Teach AI Classes</h3>
        <p>
          I teach beginner-friendly AI sessions for kids and use the money raised to support this project.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🖨️</div>
        <h3>I Create 3D printed gifts</h3>
        <p>
          I use donations to buy filament, supplies, packaging, and tools to make keychains, toys, and more.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎁</div>
        <h3>I Donate with Love</h3>
        <p>
          I want each gift to remind a child: you matter, you are loved, and your light is just beginning to rise.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <h2 class="section-title">My Vision</h2>
    <div class="story-box">
      <p>
        I dream of a world where no child grows up without warmth, kindness, or a reason to smile.
        Every gift I make has one job: to bring a smile.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">My Story</h2>
    <div class="story-box">
      <p>
        My name, Vihaan, means “the first rays of the morning sun.”
      </p>
      <p>
        When I thought about children who may not get to enjoy small moments — a toy on a birthday,
        a book to read, or a simple celebration — I wanted to do something that could become
        a little ray of light for them.
      </p>
      <p>
        That is why I started this project: one gift, one child, one ray at a time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>☀️ One gift, one child, one ray at a time.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
